+# 27 Estates — Listings Mobile App (Design Spec)
+
+**Date:** 2026-04-15
+**Status:** Design approved, pending implementation plan
+**Project location:** `D:\Listings mobile version\` (new, separate repo)
+**Parent project:** [21-estates-web](../../../) (shares Supabase backend only)
+
+---
+
+## 1. Purpose & scope
+
+A standalone consumer-facing mobile app for iOS and Android that mirrors the properties/listings experience of the 27 Estates web app, optimized for native mobile. Both public buyers and agents use the same app; agent-only features (posting, managing listings) are gated behind login + role check.
+
+**In scope (v1):**
+- Full feature parity with web `/properties` flow — browse, search, detail, bookmarks, inquiries, agent profiles, posting
+- Native Mapbox-based map search
+- Agent posting via multi-step wizard
+- Email/password auth with guest mode
+
+**Out of scope (v1):**
+- Dark mode
+- Push notifications
+- In-app chat with agents
+- EMI calculator
+- Property comparison
+- Saved searches / alerts
+- Universal-link deep linking
+- Analytics (PostHog/Mixpanel)
+- Crash reporting (Sentry) — recommended for post-M2 addition
+
+---
+
+## 2. Project identity
+
+| | |
+|---|---|
+| Directory | `D:\Listings mobile version\` |
+| npm package | `listings-mobile` |
+| Display name (home screen) | **27 Estates** |
+| iOS bundle ID | `com.twentysevenestates.listings` |
+| Android package | `com.twentysevenestates.listings` |
+| Brand assets | Lifted from web: `public/logo.png`, `logo-trimmed.png`, `logo without bg (1).png` |
+| Brand colors | Web's `globals.css` tokens (teal `#183C38`, gold `#BFA270`, warm off-white `#f9f6f3`, near-black `#0E110F`) |
+| Market | India primary (₹ formatting, BHK, RERA badges, pincode) |
+
+---
+
+## 3. Tech stack
+
+- **Expo SDK 54** (matches `mobile/`), RN 0.81, React 19
+- **TypeScript** strict
+- **expo-router v6** file-based routing
+- **@supabase/supabase-js** with `AsyncStorage` session persistence
+- **@rnmapbox/maps** for Mapbox GL
+- **expo-image** for blurhash + caching
+- **react-native-reanimated** 4, **moti**, **@gorhom/bottom-sheet** 5
+- **react-hook-form** + **zod** for forms
+- **@expo/vector-icons** + `react-native-svg` for custom SVG logo
+- **react-native-toast-message** for toasts
+- **Jest + RTL** for tests, **Maestro** for E2E smoke
+
+---
+
+## 4. Architecture
+
+### 4.1 Folder structure
+
+```
+listings-mobile/
+├── app/                        # expo-router routes
+│   ├── _layout.tsx
+│   ├── (auth)/
+│   │   ├── welcome.tsx
+│   │   ├── login.tsx
+│   │   ├── signup.tsx
+│   │   └── forgot-password.tsx
+│   ├── (tabs)/
+│   │   ├── _layout.tsx         # 4-tab bar (Home, Browse-sheet, Saved, Agents)
+│   │   ├── index.tsx           # Home feed
+│   │   ├── bookmarks.tsx
+│   │   └── agents.tsx
+│   ├── category/[type].tsx     # /category/projects | properties | commercial | warehouse
+│   ├── property/[id].tsx
+│   ├── project/[id].tsx
+│   ├── agent/[id].tsx
+│   ├── search.tsx              # Map + list
+│   ├── filters.tsx             # Modal
+│   ├── inquiry/[propertyId].tsx
+│   ├── post/                   # 5-step wizard, agent-only
+│   │   ├── _layout.tsx
+│   │   ├── photos.tsx
+│   │   ├── details.tsx
+│   │   ├── price.tsx
+│   │   ├── amenities.tsx
+│   │   └── review.tsx
+│   ├── me.tsx                  # Profile (opened from Home avatar)
+│   └── settings/
+│       ├── index.tsx
+│       ├── my-listings.tsx
+│       ├── edit-profile.tsx
+│       └── become-agent.tsx
+├── components/
+│   ├── property/               # PropertyCard, HeroCarousel, PriceBlock, StatChips, etc.
+│   ├── filters/                # FilterSheet, Chip, RangeSlider
+│   ├── map/                    # MapView, PriceMarker, MapBottomSheet
+│   ├── agent/                  # AgentCard, AgentHeader
+│   ├── nav/                    # CustomTabBar, BrowseSheet
+│   └── ui/                     # Button, Input, Pill, Skeleton, EmptyState
+├── lib/
+│   ├── supabase.ts
+│   ├── auth.ts
+│   ├── proxy-url.ts            # Ported from web
+│   └── queries/
+│       ├── properties.ts
+│       ├── projects.ts
+│       ├── bookmarks.ts
+│       ├── agents.ts
+│       ├── profiles.ts
+│       └── inquiries.ts
+├── theme/
+│   ├── colors.ts
+│   ├── typography.ts
+│   ├── spacing.ts
+│   ├── radius.ts
+│   ├── shadows.ts
+│   └── motion.ts
+├── types/
+│   └── database.ts             # Generated from Supabase
+├── hooks/
+│   ├── useAuth.ts
+│   ├── useBookmarks.ts
+│   └── useDebounce.ts
+├── assets/                     # Logo, icons, splash, fonts
+├── .env                        # EXPO_PUBLIC_* vars
+├── app.json
+├── eas.json
+├── babel.config.js
+├── tsconfig.json
+└── package.json
+```
+
+### 4.2 Boundaries between units
+
+- **`lib/queries/*`** — every Supabase call lives here. Accepts a client arg (mockable). No UI concerns. Returns `{ data, error }`.
+- **`hooks/*`** — React-level state over queries. Screens import hooks, not queries directly.
+- **`components/*`** — pure presentational; data comes through props.
+- **`app/*`** — screens orchestrate hooks + components. Minimal logic.
+- **`theme/*`** — only place where raw hex/size values live.
+
+---
+
+## 5. Navigation
+
+### 5.1 Bottom tab bar (4 items, ported 1:1 from web's `MobileNav`)
+
+| Tab | Icon | Route / Action |
+|---|---|---|
+| Home | Custom house SVG (same path as web) | `/(tabs)/index` |
+| Browse | `Grid` (lucide) | **Opens a bottom sheet**, not a screen |
+| Saved | `Heart` | `/(tabs)/bookmarks` |
+| Agents | `Users` | `/(tabs)/agents` |
+
+Styling matches [`src/components/emergent/MobileNav.module.css`](../../../src/components/emergent/MobileNav.module.css): white bg, `#ebebeb` top border, inactive `#717171`, active `#183C38`, 10px label, 600 weight.
+
+### 5.2 Browse sheet
+
+2-column grid of 4 category cards (Projects, Properties, Commercial, Warehouse). Tapping a card navigates to `/category/[type]` and closes the sheet. Teal-tinted icon tile on default, full teal on press — mirrors `.browseCategoryCard` web styles.
+
+### 5.3 Profile access
+
+Home-screen sticky header has avatar (top-left). Tap → `/me`. No Profile tab.
+
+### 5.4 Post-Property access
+
+Inside Profile (`/me`) as an "Agent tools" section. Only visible to agents. Buyers see "Become an agent" instead.
+
+---
+
+## 6. Data & auth
+
+### 6.1 Backend
+
+**Shared Supabase project** with the web — same URL, same anon key, same database, same RLS. No new Supabase project, no migrations.
+
+### 6.2 Tables consumed
+
+| Table | Purpose | Key columns |
+|---|---|---|
+| `properties` | Individual listings | `id`, `property_id`, `title`, `images`, `price`, `location`, `bedrooms`, `bathrooms`, `sqft`, `property_type`, `category`, `is_featured`, `agent_id`, `amenities`, `video_url`, `floor_plans`, `created_at` |
+| `projects` | Developer projects | `id`, `project_id`, `project_name`, `images`, `min_price`, `max_price`, `location`, `status`, `section` (`residential`/`commercial`/`warehouse`), `bhk_options`, `possession_date`, `developer_name`, `is_rera_approved`, `display_order` |
+| `user_bookmarks` | Saved items | `user_id` + (`property_id` OR `project_id`) |
+| `agents` | Agent info | `id`, `name`, contact, `photo` |
+| `profiles` | Auth profile | `id` = `auth.uid`, role fields |
+
+### 6.3 Supabase client
+
+Single shared instance (`lib/supabase.ts`) using `AsyncStorage` for session persistence. Pattern mirrors existing `mobile/src/lib/supabase.ts`.
+
+### 6.4 Type generation
+
+`npx supabase gen types typescript --project-id qjesattjnuoogqgiorws > types/database.ts`. Regenerate on schema change. Feeds `Database` generic into client for typed queries.
+
+### 6.5 Auth
+
+- Email + password (primary)
+- Password reset via email link (reuses existing web template)
+- Guest mode: no session; bookmarks in `AsyncStorage`
+- On login, guest bookmarks bulk-inserted into `user_bookmarks`, local key cleared
+- Agent gate: `profile.role === 'agent'` (exact column verified during impl)
+
+### 6.6 Auth-gated actions
+
+Guest can browse everything. Auth required for: bookmark (on first save), contact agent, post property, agent features.
+
+### 6.7 Images
+
+Images flow through `lib/proxy-url.ts` (ported verbatim from web). `expo-image` renders them with blurhash placeholders + native caching.
+
+### 6.8 Inquiries
+
+Write inquiry into Supabase `inquiries` table (create if missing). Trigger email to agent via Supabase edge function using existing `RESEND_API_KEY`. Fallback: hit web's `/api/inquiries` route if present — decided at implementation.
+
+---
+
+## 7. Theme system
+
+### 7.1 Colors (`theme/colors.ts`) — 1:1 with web
+
+```
+primary       #183C38    (deep teal)
+primaryDark   #0E2624    (pressed)
+gold          #BFA270    (luxury accent)
+goldMuted     rgba(191, 162, 112, 0.7)
+background    #f9f6f3    (warm off-white)
+backgroundWarm#FAF9F7
+surface       #FFFFFF
+surfaceAlt    #f8fafc
+textPrimary   #0E110F
+textMuted     #6F6558
+textInverse   #FFFFFF
+border        #ebebeb    (matches web tab bar)
+borderSubtle  #e2e8f0
+success       #10B981
+warning       #F59E0B
+danger        #DC2626
+inactive      #717171    (matches web nav inactive)
+```
+
+### 7.2 Typography
+
+- **Playfair Display** (400, 700) — display/hero
+- **Inter** (400, 500, 600, 700) — UI/body
+
+Sizes: 11 · 13 · 15 · 17 · 20 · 24 · 32 · 40. Loaded via `expo-font`.
+
+### 7.3 Spacing
+
+4-pt grid: 0 · 4 · 8 · 12 · 16 · 20 · 24 · 32 · 40 · 48 · 64 · 80.
+
+### 7.4 Radius
+
+`sm:6` (chips) · `md:10` (icon tiles) · `lg:14` (cards) · `xl:20` (sheets) · `2xl:24` (hero) · `full:9999`.
+
+### 7.5 Shadows / elevation
+
+Platform-abstracted (iOS `shadow*` props / Android `elevation`). Three steps (sm/md/lg) plus a `featured` gold glow variant.
+
+### 7.6 Motion
+
+Easing: `out` = `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)`, `inOut` = `cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.35, 1)`. Durations: 200 / 400 / 800ms.
+
+### 7.7 Accessibility
+
+- Tap targets min 44×44 (iOS) / 48×48 (Android)
+- Contrast: `textPrimary` on `background` = 19:1; `primary` on `background` = 10:1; gold used only for decoration
+- Respects system font scaling via native `<Text>`
+- Hit-slop `{ 8, 8, 8, 8 }` on small icons
+
+### 7.8 Dark mode
+
+**Out of scope.** Tokens structured so it can be added later without refactor.
+
+---
+
+## 8. Screens
+
+### 8.1 Home (`app/(tabs)/index.tsx`)
+
+Sticky header (avatar, brand, bell) · tap-only search bar · horizontal section tabs (All/Projects/Properties/Commercial/Warehouse) · Featured carousel (horizontal, 75% card width) · Recent Listings feed (vertical, full-width cards, pull-to-refresh, pagination 20/page).
+
+### 8.2 Property Detail (`app/property/[id].tsx`)
+
+Parallax hero carousel (4:3, swipeable, pagination dots) · transparent→solid header on scroll · back/share/bookmark buttons · Playfair display title · price block · stat chips (BHK/bath/sqft/floors) · expandable description · amenities list · floor plan · Mapbox mini-map · agent card · similar listings rail · sticky bottom CTA ("Contact Agent"). Source: web `PropertyDetailClient.tsx`.
+
+### 8.3 Project Detail (`app/project/[id].tsx`)
+
+Same pattern as Property Detail plus: developer name, BHK options chips, possession date, RERA badge, project status badge.
+
+### 8.4 Search + Map (`app/search.tsx`)
+
+Full-screen Mapbox map · price-bubble markers · collapsible Gorhom bottom sheet (snap 12%/50%/90%) listing properties in view · pan/zoom triggers debounced refetch by bbox · filters button → `/filters` · list/map toggle.
+
+### 8.5 Filters (`app/filters.tsx`)
+
+Modal with: listing type segmented · category chips · price range slider · bedroom selector · location autocomplete · amenity checklist · project status · RERA/featured toggles · sticky "Show N results" button at bottom with live count. State in `FilterContext`, chips visible on Home.
+
+### 8.6 Saved / Bookmarks (`app/(tabs)/bookmarks.tsx`)
+
+Two tabs: Properties / Projects (with counts). Same card component as Home. Guest banner: "Sign in to sync". Empty state with illustration + CTA.
+
+### 8.7 Agents list (`app/(tabs)/agents.tsx`) + detail (`app/agent/[id].tsx`)
+
+List: 2-col grid, avatar + name + rating + listing count, search bar. Detail: hero avatar, name, role, stats, call/WhatsApp buttons, bio, active-listings rail.
+
+### 8.8 Profile (`app/me.tsx`)
+
+Guest: logo + sign in/create/guest CTAs. Logged-in: avatar row · Listings section (saved / inquiries / [agent-only] post / my listings) · Account (edit profile / notifications / become-agent for buyers) · Support · Sign out · version.
+
+### 8.9 Post-a-Property wizard (`app/post/*`)
+
+5 steps: Photos → Details → Price → Location+Amenities → Review. Progress bar top · Back / Continue bottom · auto-save draft to AsyncStorage every 5s · photos use `expo-image-picker` multi-select, compressed client-side (<500KB), uploaded to Supabase storage with blurhash generated locally · Location step uses Mapbox pin-drop for exact coords · Review shows final preview before publish.
+
+### 8.10 Inquiry modal (`app/inquiry/[propertyId].tsx`)
+
+Name + phone + message form → insert into `inquiries` table + trigger email via edge function. Close on success with toast.
+
+### 8.11 Auth (`app/(auth)/*`)
+
+Welcome (logo + intro + sign in/create/guest) · Login (email, pw, forgot link) · Signup (name, email, pw, confirm) · Forgot password (email + confirmation). All brand-styled, teal CTAs.
+
+### 8.12 Category screens (`app/category/[type].tsx`)
+
+Shares layout with Home, pre-filtered:
+- `projects` → `projects` where `section='residential'`
+- `properties` → `properties` only
+- `commercial` → `projects` where `section='commercial'` + commercial-category `properties`
+- `warehouse` → `projects` where `section='warehouse'` + warehouse-category `properties`
+
+---
+
+## 9. Error handling
+
+- Query error → `react-native-toast-message` with actionable message ("Pull to refresh")
+- Auth error → inline on form
+- Offline → top banner "Reconnecting…"
+- Image load fail → fallback to `no-image.svg`
+- Form validation → zod + per-field inline errors
+
+---
+
+## 10. Testing strategy
+
+| Layer | Tool | Covers |
+|---|---|---|
+| Unit | Jest + ts-jest | `lib/queries/*`, helpers (price formatting, filter builders, proxy URL) |
+| Component | RN Testing Library | `PropertyCard` bookmark behavior, `FilterSheet` state, `PostWizard` step transitions, auth forms |
+| E2E smoke | Maestro (YAML) | Launch → browse → open property → bookmark → sign up → saw bookmark synced |
+
+Explicitly not tested: Supabase internals, exact pixel positioning, Mapbox rendering (manual QA).
+
+---
+
+## 11. Dev workflow
+
+```
+npx expo start                        # Metro + QR
+npx expo run:android                  # dev build
+npx expo run:ios                      # dev build (Mac)
+npm test                              # Jest + RTL
+maestro test .maestro/smoke.yaml      # E2E
+npm run typecheck                     # tsc --noEmit
+npm run lint                          # eslint + prettier
+```
+
+Reanimated + Mapbox require a dev build (not Expo Go). Use **EAS Build** for development/preview/production.
+
+---
+
+## 12. Release plan
+
+### M1 — Skeleton
+Project scaffolded · navigation renders (4 tabs + stack) · theme applied · Supabase connects · Home renders mock list · runs on Android sim + iOS sim.
+
+### M2 — Core browse
+Home with real data + section tabs + featured rail + pagination · Property Detail · Browse sheet + category screens · Bookmarks (guest + logged-in sync) · Auth flow. **Ship to TestFlight internal + Play Store internal track.**
+
+### M3 — Search, Agents, Inquiries
+Search screen with Mapbox + markers + bottom sheet · Filters modal · Agents list + detail · Inquiry modal with email notification.
+
+### M4 — Agent features + Polish
+Post-a-property wizard · My Listings · Profile edit, notification settings · Perf pass (image preload, list virtualization, marker clustering) · Accessibility audit · **Submit to App Store + Play Store.**
+
+---
+
+## 13. Known risks & mitigations
+
+| Risk | Mitigation |
+|---|---|
+| Mapbox token not in `.env.local` | Obtain before M3; `EXPO_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN` required |
+| RLS gaps for mobile access patterns | Review web RLS during M2; rely on same policies |
+| App Store review (real estate extra scrutiny) | Ensure privacy policy + account-deletion flow shipped by M2 |
+| Image upload size over mobile networks | Client-side compress to <500KB before upload |
+| Mapbox pricing at scale | Monitor map loads; current free tier 50k/mo |
+| Inquiry email deliverability | Use existing web `RESEND_API_KEY` + domain |
+
+---
+
+## 14. Future enhancements (post-v1)
+
+- Dark mode
+- Push notifications (listing alerts, inquiry replies)
+- In-app chat with agents
+- EMI calculator
+- Property comparison (2-up)
+- Saved searches + email/push alerts
+- Universal links (tap web link → opens app to same property)
+- PostHog / Mixpanel analytics
+- Sentry crash reporting
+- OAuth providers (Google, Apple Sign-in)
+- Video walkthroughs / live virtual tours
+
+---
+
+## 15. Decisions explicitly deferred to implementation
+
+1. **`profiles.role` vs separate `agents` table** for role check — verify during M2.
+2. **`inquiries` table schema** — verify or create during M3 with the email-via-edge-function approach.
+3. **Exact Mapbox Studio style URL** — picked during M3 when the map screen is built.
+4. **Exact splash screen dimensions + icon sizes** — generated during M1 from logo source.
+
+---
+
